long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Google Docs Quick Create Extension Quickly Creates Google Docs, Sheets, Slides & More – Right From Your Browser!

Easily generate new Google Drive documents directly from your browser bar with just one click. This extension adds a simple menu that allows you to quickly create:

- Google Docs
- Google Sheets
- Google Slides
- Google Forms

Streamline your workflow by accessing Google Drive’s most-used tools instantly. Perfect for professionals, students, and anyone who wants faster access to Google’s suite of productivity apps!
